name: Second whale hunting expedition
description: A longer trip expedition that searches for whale traces that could be up to 30 days old. I discovered that you could train dogs to detect whale poop. Well, we have a trained dog with us and his name is Theo. This boat is powered by the TzKT API and it might not work in the future if the API calls change. Creator: Javier Gracia Carpio | @jagracar
